title: The Freaks of AHS review Coven
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: My order would be Coven, Murder House, Asylum. I feel the alien storyline makes me dislike Asylum if you just rank the first 3 seasons.
I have always loved Stevie Nicks. I got a kick out of her being a part of Coven.

Also 
Queenie was part of the council by the end of Coven. Queenie went to LA to be on the price is 
Right game show but died at the hotel Cortez.  Cordelia has to get her best witches to go to LA and she goes with them.  And all HELL breaks loose. This can give way to a cameo by the Countess and the Hotel Cortez itself. Also in the announcement to me the babies skin is like the rubbermans suit. Making me believe that it is Micheal Langdon. Remember Ryan uses symbolism for the teasers. Nothing is ever literal.
The echo was like nails on a chalkboard

There is ginormous plot hole in the season that always never made since. Tituba supposedly taught the Salem witches magic in 1692. So how come Prudence Mather and her coven, which was in the same year of 1692, develop magic so fast and have a supreme if Tituba taught them. It would've have made more since if Tituba was the Supreme of Salem, rather than Prudence Mather.
